00:03:05.989 --> 00:03:09.620
Should these impacts have been powerful enough,
chunks of Earth's crust would've been kicked

00:03:09.620 --> 00:03:10.939
into space.

00:03:10.939 --> 00:03:14.700
As the planet is covered in life, some of
these chunks of Earth rock would've likely

00:03:14.700 --> 00:03:16.470
had bacteria hitching a ride.

